data.description: Beautiful home located in a very sought-after, quiet, & well established neighborhood! This updated brick home features 4 bedrooms /2 full baths w/ a nice office/work-out area that can serve as a 5th bedroom. Situated on an oversized corner lot too! Over half an acre! Outside features a large covered front porch, 3 car carport, fire pit, dog run/kennel, & more! Large eat-in kitchen with lots of cabinets, counter-top work space, stainless appliances, pantry, & oversize utility room. Kitchen is open to large living & dining area with WBFP. Living area & front office have wood floors! The Master suite is spacious & boast a LARGE walk-in shower! Home has had many updates! NEW ROOF & BRAND NEW HVAC system as well. Don’t miss this chance to be part of this family-friendly neighborhood! You'll want to make this home! Definitely going to want to check this one out soon! Call today!
